text: Group L of the 2019 Africa Cup of Nations qualification tournament will be one of the 12 groups to decide the teams which qualify for the 2019 Africa Cup of Nations finals tournament. The group consists of four teams: Cape Verde, Uganda, Tanzania, and Lesotho. ==Standings== ==Matches== \---- \---- \---- \---- \---- ==Goalscorers== ;3 goals * Farouk Miya ;2 goals * Ricardo Gomes * Mbwana Samatta * Emmanuel Okwi ;1 goal * Djaniny * Stopira * Sera Motebang * Thapelo Tale * Simon Msuva * Geoffrey Sserunkuma ==Notes== ==References== Group L
